who has visited the Cold Palace?

23
00:01:06,230 --> 00:01:06,870
Your Majesty,

24
00:01:07,080 --> 00:01:08,160
as far as I know,

25
00:01:08,360 --> 00:01:10,310
Consort Mu came once.

26
00:01:10,590 --> 00:01:12,230
But I didn't see

27
00:01:12,510 --> 00:01:13,910
if she brought any cakes.

28
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:15,510
What did I say?

29
