33
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:24,440
Like I said,

34
00:01:25,190 --> 00:01:26,310
without sufficient evidence,

35
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:27,510
we mustn't convict anyone!

36
00:01:27,870 --> 00:01:28,720
Murder is a serious crime.

37
00:01:29,550 --> 00:01:31,000
I'll have it carefully investigated.

38
